regions.today: Staying mostly cloudy with patches of drizzle but a good deal of dry weather overall. Highest temperatures of 11 to 13 degrees in light southeast winds.

regions.tonight: Mainly dry tonight with just patches of isolated drizzle. Mainly cloudy with the odd clear spell. Lowest temperatures of 7 to 11 degrees in light to moderate east to southeast winds.

regions.tomorrow: Cloudy tomorrow with patches of mist and drizzle. Some brighter spells developing for a time in the afternoon. Highest temperatures of 13 to 16 degrees in light to moderate southerly winds.
